where id = object_id('WorkPaper')
and type = 'U')

/* Table: WorkPaper */
/*==============================================================*/
create table WorkPaper (
ID integer identity,
ProdCode varchar(50) not null,
WorkGuidanceImg image null,
constraint PK_WORKPAPER primary key (ProdCode)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'作业指导书',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'WorkPaper'
go
